---
import Engineer from "@src/assets/Mary/Mary.webp";
import Logo from "@src/assets/svg/logo.astro";
---

<div class="min-w-full h-full relative">
  <img
    src={Engineer.src}
    alt="Ingeniera en muestra"
    class="absolute inset-0 size-full object-cover object-center brightness-85"
  />
  <article
    class="absolute z-1 size-full flex flex-col gap-6 justify-center items-center"
  >
    <Logo class="size-28 text-white m-10" />
    <h1
      class="text-6xl font-playfair text-red-950 drop-shadow-md drop-shadow-gray-200/50"
    >
      EL INICIO
    </h1>
    <span
      class="h-16 w-0.75 border border-red-950 bg-red-950 drop-shadow-md drop-shadow-gray-200/50"
    ></span>
    <p
      class="max-w-5xl text-[32px] text-center font-playfair text-red-950 drop-shadow-md drop-shadow-gray-200/50"
    >
      Luméa nace como un estudio de diseño de interiores enfocado en crear
      espacios funcionales y estéticos, apoyados en la visualización 3D.
    </p>
  </article>
</div>
